creator: VOOP LLC
descriptionHtml:
Voop is an Azerbaijani brand that represents a fast and convenient food delivery service.

What are our advantages?

Wide choice of restaurants.
With Voop, you will have access to a menu of hundreds of restaurants and cafes of national and foreign cuisine. Here you will always find something delicious!

Free delivery.
Upon registration, each user will receive a whole month of free delivery from every single restaurant on our application. In addition user will receive 15% cashback from the very first order.

Live tracking.
With Voop, you can easily track delivery by watching the order status in real time. We take into account all factors - from cooking time to weather conditions and traffic jams.

Delivery time.
Get your favorite meals faster with Voop delivery service. Our main goal is to deliver the meal as fast as possible.

Payment methods.
We guarantee secure payment in any way convenient for you - not only by credit card, but also in cash and using Voop balance.


Special deals.
Voop regularly offers special deals with various restaurants that will surely delight users.
Also, when registering, each user has his own unique invitation code. Share the promo with a friend and you both will receive cashback.

Your precious time is our priority. We will do our best to keep it for something important.
descriptionShort: Order delicious food from the restaurants you love with Voop delivery.
